snippet.title: The Strongest TOFU - Official Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Take a look at the Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer for The Strongest TOFU, an action platformer developed by Zounashi Games. Players will choose between firm, silken, and freeze-dried tofu to leap, dodge, and twirl toward the bowl of piping-hot soup at the end of each level. Dodge hungry animals and sizzling hot frying pans to become the one and only tofu master. The Strongest TOFU is available now for Nintendo Switch alongside PC.
